      "title": "Combine like terms",
      "content": "The terms $8x$ and $-7x$ combine to $x$.<br/>$$8x-7x+130=260$$<br/>$$x+130=260$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Isolate the variable",
      "content": "Subtract $130$ from both sides.<br/>$$x=130$$"
